# Editing with ArcGIS Pro

__Getting started with ArcGIS Pro:__ [ArcGIS Pro help](https://pro.arcgis.com/en/pro-app/help/main/welcome-to-the-arcgis-pro-app-help.htm)

Things to consider
 - Will you be in a connected environment when editing?
 - Will you be collaboratively editing, where others will be editing at the same time?
 - There are many ways to work with GIS, below is one approach to editing.

### Creating a Feature class 

1. Be sure that you are signed in to ArcGIS Pro.

2. Create a new project (select Map)  

